<Link id="l00032" /><CodeLine lineNumber="32"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// ScheduleDAGSDNodes - A ScheduleDAG for scheduling SDNode-based DAGs.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00033" /><CodeLine lineNumber="33"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00034" /><CodeLine lineNumber="34"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// Edges between SUnits are initially based on edges in the SelectionDAG,</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00035" /><CodeLine lineNumber="35"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// and additional edges can be added by the schedulers as heuristics.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00036" /><CodeLine lineNumber="36"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// SDNodes such as Constants, Registers, and a few others that are not</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00037" /><CodeLine lineNumber="37"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// interesting to schedulers are not allocated SUnits.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00038" /><CodeLine lineNumber="38"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00039" /><CodeLine lineNumber="39"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// SDNodes with MVT::Glue operands are grouped along with the flagged</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00040" /><CodeLine lineNumber="40"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// nodes into a single SUnit so that they are scheduled together.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00041" /><CodeLine lineNumber="41"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00042" /><CodeLine lineNumber="42"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// SDNode-based scheduling graphs do not use SDep::Anti or SDep::Output</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00043" /><CodeLine lineNumber="43"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// edges.  Physical register dependence information is not carried in</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00044" /><CodeLine lineNumber="44"><Highlight kind="comment">  /// the DAG and must be handled explicitly by schedulers.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00045" /><CodeLine lineNumber="45"><Highlight kind="comment">  ///</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
